ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25a5acdf76bbb0b7990aee3806d3438bf3869093","tid":1568953,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbdb234e3403ef6cdf0e0dad2516a8efea11406f","tid":1568953,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:33:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:34:33.000Z","msg":"你又知<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:35:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:38:42.000Z","msg":"我0.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa0e70c9898a2d462d847b5f65e6f7cea7474065","tid":1568953,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:41:11.000Z","msg":"【終極核彈】《願榮光》之後－成立海外臨時民主政府<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1566796\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1566796</a><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光》之後。。。<br />\n天滅中共 平反六四！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">海外臨時政府 自由香港<br />\nFREE HONG KONG</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/freehongkonghkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffreehongkonghkg&d=DHtl%2BAGMG05sKYyicqAXSuL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=184b880e\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/freehongkonghkg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/nBMTNBB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnBMTNBB.jpg&h=16392072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n讓這攬炒旗隨風飄揚！（logo已獲攬炒巴授權使用）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人哋北韓都做到 香港唔係做唔到呀嘛？</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共已經決定企硬，連溫和到咁既五大訴求都唔會接受。咁呢個政府仲有咩面代表人民<br />\n<br />\n擇個好日子揀個好地方，設立海外臨時政府<br />\n<br />\n目標係「要使國際社會廣泛相信港共政府為非法政權，爭取外國政府支持，替天行道，天滅中共」<br />\n「因應警察濫用暴力+濫捕事件於國際組織上追究」<br />\n<br />\n最後「推動香港進入real autonomy 嘅時代」<br />\n<br />\n因為而家我哋已經無嘢可以好輸，如果我哋就咁俾場運動完結，最後受害，被批鬥，被清算係每一個真。香港人。前線於是，和理非也如是。警察已經將文革係各中小學重演，唔駛好耐就會到其他界別。"},{"pid":"4b5f5b0117bdd804deecadd0c2a8ef0602eb19c3","tid":1568953,"uid":130898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:41:47.000Z","msg":"入面D歌詞仲係奴才心態<br />\n<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">盼</span>自由 歸於 這裡<br />\n<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港<br />\n<br />\n在晚星 墜落 徬徨午夜<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處吹來 號角聲<br />\n捍自由 來齊集這裡 來全力抗對<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也永不滅<br />\n<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">祈求</span> 民主與自由 萬世都不朽<br />\n我<span style=\"color: red;\">願</span>榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n自由民主係要自己爭取<br />\n而唔係願 祈求 盼<br />\n<br />\n我唔反動唱歌 但唱歌要配合實質行動"},{"pid":"6e445a60d256b9dbd29561b6bcafdf9ec5601321","tid":1568953,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"567bc79b3d9130eb2ae2cd29fd9ea507d869ec31","tid":1568953,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b916cdab56d5bbdcf65eeb2b8ff2c256a8701088","tid":1568953,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:38:13.000Z","msg":"幾時有得放上itunes <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:41:58.000Z","msg":"整緊~"},{"pid":"69f0aebc72b6cc3d5f5d205de55cf7811c94e1e2","tid":1568953,"uid":264697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:50:15.